high_descs: walk forward to counter top between fridge and stove
pick up fork from counter top
turn right, walk to kitchen sink, turn to face counter top between stove and sink
open cabinet above the counter top, put fork on dish inside cabinet
pick up dish from inside cabinet, close cabinet doors
turn around walk to counter top with red toaster on top, stop in front of counter
put dish on counter top to the left of the red toaster
anns.task_desc: pick up fork and dish, put them next to red toaster on counter top

high_descs: Turn right, head straight to the stove
Pick up the fork on the side of the stove
Turn right, head to the sink
Open the cabinet door above the sink
Put the fork on a plate in the cabinet
Take the plate out of the cabinet, Turn around
walk to the toaster, put the plate on the counter next to the toaster
anns.task_desc: Put the fork on plate next to the toaster

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, then turn left to go to the counter between the fridge and the oven.
Pick up the fork on the counter, to the right of the knife.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left near the sink.
In the cabinet above the electric socket, put the fork on the plate.
Take the plate from the cabinet.
Turn around, then turn left to face the dishwasher.
Place the plate on the counter, directly above the dishwasher and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a fork on it on the counter.
